quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,(Aey Nabi) kya humne tumhara seena tumhare liye khol nahin diya
  94,2,Aur tumpar se woh bhari bojh utar diya
  94,3,Jo tumhari qamar todhe daal raha tha
  94,4,Aur tumhare khatir tumharey zikr ka awazah buland kar diya
  94,5,Pas haqeeqat yeh hai kay tangi kay saat farakhi bhi hai
  94,6,Beshak tangi kay saath farakhi bhi hai
  94,7,Lihaza jab tum faarig ho to Ibadat ki mushakkat mei lag jao
  94,8,Aur apne Rubb ki taraf raagib ho
  95,1,Kasam hai Injir(fig) ki aur Zaitun ki
  95,2,Aur Tur-e-sina (Mount Sinai)
  95,3,Aur is pur-aman shehar (Makkah) ki
  95,4,Humne Insan ko behtarin saakht par paida kiya
  95,5,Phir usey ulta pher kar humne sab neechon se neech kar diya
  95,6,Siwaye un logon ke jo iman laye aur neik amal karte rahey kay unke liye kabhi khatam na hone wala ajar hai
  95,7,Pas (aey nabi) iske baad kaun jaza o saza ke maamle mei tumko jhutla sakta hai
  95,8,Kya Allah sab hakimon se bada hakim nahin hai
  96,1,Padho (Aey Nabi) apne Rubb ke naam ke saath Jisne paida kiya
  96,2,Jamey huey khoon ke ek lothdey se Insan ki takhliq ki
  96,3,Padho aur tumhara Rubb bada kareem hai
  96,4,jisne qalam ke zariya se ilm sikhaya
  96,5,Insan ko woh ilm diya jisey woh na jaanta tha
  96,6,"Hargiz nahin, Insan sarkahshi karta hai"
  96,7,Is bina par ke woh apne aap ko be niyaz dekhta hai
  96,8,(halaanke) palatna yaqeenan tere Rubb hi ki taraf hai
  96,9,Tumne dekha us shaks ko
  96,10,Jo ek banday ko mana karta hai jabke woh namaz padta ho
  96,11,Tumhara kya khayal hai agar (woh banda) raah e raast par ho
  96,12,ya parhezgari ki talqeen karta ho
  96,13,Tumhara kya khayal hai agar (yeh mana karne wala shakhs haqq ko) jhutlata aur mooh moadta ho
  96,14,Kya woh nahin jaanta ke Allah dekh raha hai
  96,15,Hargiz nahin agar woh baaz na aaya to hum uski peshani ke baal pakad kar usey khinchey ge
  96,16,Us peshani ko jo jhooti aur sakth khatakaar hai
  96,17,Woh bulaley apne haamiyon ki toli ko
  96,18,Hum bhi azaab ke farishton ko bula lengey
  96,19,"Hargiz nahin, uski baat na mano aur sajda karo aur (apne Rubb ka) qurb hasil karo"
  97,1,Humne is (Quran) ko shab-e-qadr mei nazil kiya hai
  97,2,Aur tum kya jano kay shab-e-qadr kya hai
  97,3,Shab-e-qadr hazar mahino se zyada behtar hai
  97,4,Farishtey aur rooh(Jibrael) us mein apne Rubb ke izn(permission) se har hukm le kar utarte hai
  97,5,Woh raat sarasar salamati hai tulu e fajr tak
  98,1,Ehle kitab aur Mushrikin mein se jo log kafir thay (woh apne kufr se) baaz aane walay na thay jab tak ke unke paas dalil e roshan na aa jaye
  98,2,(Yani) Allah ke taraf se ek Rasool jo paak sahife padh kar sunaye
  98,3,Jin mein bilkul raast aur durust tehrirein likhi hui ho
  98,4,Pehle jin logon ko kitab di gayi thi unmei tafarqa barpa(split/divide) nahin hua magar is ke baad ke un ke paas (raahe rast ka) bayan e wazeh aa chuka tha
  98,5,"Aur unko iske siwa koi hukum nahin diya gaya tha ke Allah ke bandagi karein apne deen ko uske liye khalis karke. Bilkul yaksu ho kar, Aur namaz qayam karein aur zakat de yahi nihayat sahih-o-durust deen hai"
  98,6,"Ehle kitaab aur mushrikin mein se jin logon ne kufr kiya hai woh yaqeenan jahannam ki aag mein jayenge aur hamesha us mein rahenge, yeh log badh-tareen e khalayek(creation) hain"
  98,7,Jo log iman le aaye aur jinhon nay neik amal kiye woh yaqeenan behtareen-e-khalayeq hai
  98,8,Unki jaza unke Rubb ke yahan dayimi(eternal) qayam ki jannatein hain jinke nichey nehrein beh rahi hongi. Woh unmein hamesha hamesh rahenge. Allah unse razi hua aur woh Allah se razi huey. Yeh kuch hai us shaks ke liye jisne apne Rubb ka khauf kiya ho
  99,1,Jab zameen apni puri shiddat kay saath hila daali jayegi
  99,2,Aur zameen apne andar kay sarey bojh nikal kar bahar daal degi
  99,3,Aur Insan kahega ke yeh isko kya ho raha hai
  99,4,Us roz woh apne (upar guzre huey) halaat bayan karegi
  99,5,Kyunke tere Rubb ne usey (aisa karne ka) hukm diya hoga
  99,6,Us roz log mutafarrik halat mein paltenge taakay unke aamal unko dikhaey jayein
  99,7,Phir jisne zarra barabar neki ki hogi woh usko dekh lega
  99,8,Aur jisne zarra barabar badi ki hogi woh usko dekh lega
  100,1,Kasam hai un (ghodon) ki jo phunkare marte hue dhaudte hai
  100,2,Phir (apne tapon se) chingariyan jhaadte hain
  100,3,Phir subah sawere chapa marte hain
  100,4,Phir is mauke par gard o gubar udatey hai
  100,5,Phir isi halat mei kisi majmey ke andar ja ghustey hai
  100,6,Haqiqat yeh hai ke Insan apne Rubb ka bada nashukra hai
  100,7,Aur woh khud is par gawah hai
  100,8,Aur woh maal-o-daulat ki muhabbat mei buri tarah mubtala hai